{"tid":1116211,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"內地票房！《P風暴》衝7億！ DC《沙贊》難破3億！","createTime":"2019-04-19T18:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T14:06:35.000Z","uid":167658,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd5ededb33f29f8ee1dca966922c207ccc7c72f","tid":1116211,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:25:22.000Z","msg":"《P風暴》將刷新該系列的票房紀錄，未來票房更有希望衝擊6億大關，很有希望超越古天樂個人票房成績最佳：《使徒行者》6.06億元<br />\n<br />\n而相比北美大賣5300萬美元的亮眼表現，《沙贊！ 》在中國的口碑和票房表現只能用慘淡來形容<br />\n<br />\n儘管1.03億的首日票房在DC電影宇宙中開畫成績僅次於《正義聯盟》，<span style=\"color: red;\">但斷崖般的口碑，讓影片週六6730萬、週日3480萬的票房走勢完全可以用&ldquo;斷崖式跌幅&rdquo;來形容</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以目前的票房走势来看，《沙赞》很有可能取代《超人：钢铁之躯》3.98亿元，成为DC超级英雄作，在中国内地票房最低的作品。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本身Shazam掂硬，㸃解大陸人迫害DC</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de411dbf27a74f12575781583ad56065c2081a62","tid":1116211,"uid":167658,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igB0qLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigB0qLk.png&h=21b6d082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大陸人迫害DC</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37b9ee773014cb29754fa0f51381beafa309839","tid":1116211,"uid":103230,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"superhero fans base 至少5億票房<br />\n4億都冇既=仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gi